/span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-认知\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">ADHD</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-04-10</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">爱孩子的真实样子，<br>当教育孩子的过程不顺利时，<br>努力记住这一点。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心的孩子这样教》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第2章，第12页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-成长\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">ADHD</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-04-10</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">父母爱孩子最有效的方式就是注意到他这个人，<br>注意到他做了什么。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心的孩子这样教》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第2章，第13页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-治愈\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">ADHD</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-04-10</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">只要你持续地爱孩子，<br>并信任这份爱，<br>几年之后，<br>孩子的优势自然会出现。<br>如果没有爱，<br>优势或是无法出现，<br>或是受到扭曲。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心的孩子这样教》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第2章，第14页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-冷静\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-top\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-tags\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-tag\">ADHD</span></div>\n        <time class=\"zhaizhai-date\">2026-04-10</time>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-content-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-content\">优势取向可以带来希望、热情和正向能量，<br>而缺陷取向则会消灭希望、浇熄热情，<br>并让正向能量消失。</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-source\">—— 节选自《分心的孩子这样教》</div>\n        <div class=\"zhaizhai-meta\">\n          <span class=\"zhaizhai-loc\">第4章，第23页</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-back container\">\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-header\"><span class=\"zhaizhai-back-title\">思考卡片</span></div>\n      <div class=\"zhaizhai-back-body\"><section class=\"zhaizhai-back-section zhaizhai-back-empty\">暂无 insight</section></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(() => {\n  let flipSwitchTimer = null\n\n  document.addEventListener('click', event => {\n    if (event.target.closest('a')) return\n    const card = event.target.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail .zhaizhai-flip-card')\n    if (!card) return\n    if (flipSwitchTimer) {\n      clearTimeout(flipSwitchTimer)\n      flipSwitchTimer = null\n    }\n    const container = card.closest('.zhaizhai-reading-detail')\n    const cards = container ? container.querySelectorAll('.zhaizhai-flip-card.is-flipped') : []\n    const isFlipped = card.classList.contains('is-flipped')\n\n    cards.forEach(item => {\n      if (item !== card) item.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    })\n\n    if (isFlipped) {\n      card.classList.remove('is-flipped')\n    } else {\n      const hasOtherFlipped = [...cards].some(item => item !== card)\n      if (hasOtherFlipped) {\n        // Close previous card first, then open target card for smoother switch.\n        flipSwitchTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n          card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n          flipSwitchTimer = null\n        }, 120)\n      } else {\n        card.classList.add('is-flipped')\n      }\n    }\n  })\n})()\n</script>\n</body></html>","raw":"---\ntitle: 分心的孩子这样教\ndate: 2026-05-19 08:24:47\ntype: page\naside: true\ncomments: false\n---\n\n> 共 6 条摘录，最近更新：2026-04-10\n\n<div class=\"zhaizhai-masonry zhaizhai-reading-detail\">\n<div class=\"shuoshuo-item zhaizhai-item x-mood-认知\">\n  <div class=\"zhaizhai-flip-card\">\n    <div class=\"zhaizhai-face zhaizhai-face-front container\">\n      <div class=\